Luigi Costa is accused of killing his elderly neighbour Terrence Freebody in Red Hill, Canberra in July 2012 . 
  The 71-year-old was believed to be suffering from dementia and alcohol abuse at the time of the murder . 
  Forensic psychiatrist examined Costa after the attack and found evidence of his state of mind declining in the lead-up to the killing . 
  Costa was accused of stomping on his neighbour's head, cutting his throat and stabbing him multiple times in the dining room of his home . 
  He is charged with murder and is on trial in Canberra . 
 